704688f-a.title: Brooklyn: Grand Street - Driggs Avenue
704688f-a.text:
Grand Street, north side, east from Driggs Ave. Also seen.is Driggs
Ave., east side, north from Grand Strcet, showing the whole corner devoted to
instalment selling by Whalen Bros.
August 9, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
